HOST: http://polls.apiblueprint.org/

# liberato-luglio-esame

Polls is a simple API allowing consumers to view polls and vote in them.

## Questions Collection [/questions]

### List All Teams [GET]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        [
            {
                "teamID": "01",
                "name": "Croazia",
                "is_still_in": true,
                "matches": [
                    {
                        "opponent": "Italy",
