        ]

### Create a Team [POST]

Inserisci una nuova squadra

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "teamID": "02",
            "name": "Brazil",
            "is_still_in": true,
            "matches": [
                {
                        "opponent": "France",
                        "outcome": "W"
                }, {
                        "opponent": "Belgium",
                        "outcome": "W"
                    }
                ]
        }

